# Global Rules for MSP Repository

## Language Requirement (MANDATORY)
**ALL OUTPUT MUST BE IN CHINESE (简体中文).**
Always respond in Chinese regardless of the input language.
Technical terms (e.g., variable names, command lines) should remain in English.

## Project Context
This is the MSP (Media Share & Preview) project.
- Backend: Go (Golang)
- Frontend: Vite + Vanilla JS (No Frameworks)

